# Node
node_modules/
dist/
# v4 exception — the Pi UI dist is the SHIPPED artifact (the v4 source
# lives in the private cloud monorepo's frontend/packages/pi-ui/; we
# distribute the built bundle via this public submodule). Allow
# ui/dist/ specifically so the Pi can fetch + serve the v4 UI.
!ui/dist/
!ui/dist/**

